---
import SubpageLayout from '../../../layouts/SubpageLayout.astro';
---

<SubpageLayout
  lang="en"
  title="Implementation Guidance"
  subtitle="Hands-on guidance during AI rollout. Change management, adoption tracking and on-the-floor coaching."
  seoDescription="AI Implementation Guidance: hands-on support during AI rollout. Change management, adoption tracking and coaching on the work floor. By AI Heroes."
  accentColor="red"
  pillarBadge="Consulting"
  ctaLabel="Schedule a consultation"
  trustedBy={["Medux", "Trabu", "OLX Poland"]}
>
  <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-serif text-brand-dark mb-6">The bridge between plan and reality</h2>

    <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
      You have an AI strategy, maybe even a working prototype. But the real challenge starts now: how do you get people to actually use it? AI implementation rarely fails on the tech. Adoption is almost always the bottleneck. We guide your team through the entire rollout.
    </p>

    <div class="bg-stone-50 p-6 md:p-8 mb-8 border-l-4 border-brand-red not-prose">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-serif text-brand-dark mb-3">What we do</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-stone-600 list-disc ml-5">
        <li>Change management strategy and communication plan</li>
        <li>Coaching of key users and champions on the work floor</li>
        <li>Adoption monitoring with concrete metrics</li>
        <li>Identifying and addressing resistance</li>
        <li>Adapting work processes to new tooling</li>
        <li>Setting up feedback loops between users and development team</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-serif text-brand-dark mb-4">How we guide</h3>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-8 not-prose">
      <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-stone-200"><div class="text-4xl font-serif text-brand-red mb-3">1</div><h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark mb-2">Preparation</h4><p class="text-sm text-stone-600">Stakeholder mapping, communication plan and identification of champions per department.</p></div>
      <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-stone-200"><div class="text-4xl font-serif text-brand-red mb-3">2</div><h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark mb-2">Rollout</h4><p class="text-sm text-stone-600">Phased introduction with guidance on the work floor. Coaching, demos and hands-on support.</p></div>
      <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-stone-200"><div class="text-4xl font-serif text-brand-red mb-3">3</div><h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark mb-2">Embedding</h4><p class="text-sm text-stone-600">Measuring adoption, adjusting where needed and preparing your internal team to continue independently.</p></div>
    </div>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-serif text-brand-dark mb-4">Why implementation guidance?</h3>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8 not-prose">
      <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-stone-200"><h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark mb-2">70% fail without it</h4><p class="text-sm text-stone-600">For most AI projects, the bottleneck is adoption and change management. Technology is rarely the problem.</p></div>
      <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-stone-200"><h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark mb-2">Faster adoption</h4><p class="text-sm text-stone-600">With targeted guidance, your team goes 2-3x faster from 'struggling' to 'second nature'.</p></div>
      <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-stone-200"><h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark mb-2">Less resistance</h4><p class="text-sm text-stone-600">By involving employees early and taking concerns seriously, you prevent pushback.</p></div>
      <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-stone-200"><h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark mb-2">Measurable results</h4><p class="text-sm text-stone-600">We track adoption metrics so you know whether the investment is paying off.</p></div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-8 not-prose">
      <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white border border-stone-200"><div class="text-3xl font-serif text-brand-red mb-2">2-8 weeks</div><div class="text-sm text-stone-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Guidance period</div></div>
      <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white border border-stone-200"><div class="text-3xl font-serif text-brand-red mb-2">On-site</div><div class="text-sm text-stone-500 uppercase tracking-wider">At your workplace</div></div>
      <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white border border-stone-200"><div class="text-3xl font-serif text-brand-red mb-2">Measurable</div><div class="text-sm text-stone-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Adoption tracking</div></div>
    </div>

    <div class="dark-box-content bg-brand-dark p-8 border-l-4 border-brand-blue my-8 not-prose">
      <h3>The complete picture</h3>
      <p>Implementation guidance works best combined with <a href="/en/services/ai-foundations" class="text-white underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-white/80">training for your team</a> and optionally <a href="/en/services/custom-ai-solutions" class="text-white underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-white/80">custom tooling</a> if the standard solution doesn't fit.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</SubpageLayout>
